WEBVTT

00:32.406 --> 00:33.615
Thomas?

00:34.200 --> 00:35.451
Easy now.

00:37.120 --> 00:38.620
Sleep, child.

00:39.873 --> 00:41.373
Sleep.

00:52.552 --> 00:53.927
So the killer is still out there?

00:53.970 --> 00:56.764
Yeah. Probably crawled back
to the freaks that sent her after us.

00:57.599 --> 00:59.433
Did you have to quit being a cop?

00:59.642 --> 01:03.062
- How can that help?
- Alison, this isn't why I called.

01:04.147 --> 01:07.107
I want to thank you for helping with Kira.

01:07.567 --> 01:08.650
Oh.

01:08.818 --> 01:12.529
Yeah, I get to see her
tomorrow and you set that up. So...

01:12.614 --> 01:14.114
Well, she's a special little girl.

01:15.533 --> 01:17.034
I can tell. You're very lucky.

01:31.549 --> 01:32.758
No!

02:14.717 --> 02:16.260
- Hey!
- Beth, stop. it's me.

02:16.344 --> 02:17.928
Oh, my God!

02:18.012 --> 02:19.263
You asshole!

02:19.389 --> 02:20.931
You'd stab me in the eye with a nail file?

02:21.015 --> 02:22.724
Yeah! You sneak up on me in the shower,

02:22.767 --> 02:24.893
I am going to stab you
in the eye with a nail file.

02:26.104 --> 02:27.938
Aren't you supposed to be at Cody's?

02:28.439 --> 02:30.774
I didn't mean to scare you. I'm sorry.

02:32.443 --> 02:33.944
How sorry are you?

02:34.279 --> 02:35.487
Beth...

02:36.156 --> 02:37.364
Get in.

02:54.215 --> 02:55.424
Beth.

02:56.176 --> 02:57.259
Hmm?

02:59.429 --> 03:00.929
Let's go away.

03:03.933 --> 03:05.767
You're off the force,

03:06.978 --> 03:08.604
I hate my job.

03:10.773 --> 03:12.608
Let's pack our bags.

03:13.610 --> 03:14.776
Right now.

03:16.196 --> 03:17.613
I'm serious.

03:24.579 --> 03:26.997
Let's talk about it in the morning.

03:51.564 --> 03:52.689
Now, let's put it in now!

05:41.549 --> 05:45.052
- Hey, do you want coffee?
- Uh, no thanks.

05:59.859 --> 06:01.443
How you feeling?

06:02.445 --> 06:03.653
What?

06:07.450 --> 06:09.576
No gun, no badge...

06:10.244 --> 06:11.620
- Nowhere to be.
- Hmm?

06:12.121 --> 06:13.538
Let's leave.

06:14.290 --> 06:15.707
We don't have any ties.

06:17.043 --> 06:19.461
I have three simple words for you.

06:20.129 --> 06:21.797
Rio de Janeiro.

06:22.131 --> 06:25.592
We cannot just leave now
and think about going to Rio.

06:25.927 --> 06:27.135
Why not?

06:27.762 --> 06:28.970
It's what you wanted, right?

06:29.347 --> 06:30.639
Commitment? I'm ready.

06:31.724 --> 06:33.642
I can't think about this right now.

06:34.477 --> 06:36.770
- What's wrong?
- Nothing's wrong.

06:36.813 --> 06:37.854
You're shaking like a leaf.

06:37.980 --> 06:41.274
- Where are you going?
- I'm just going out for some air. Okay?

06:46.114 --> 06:49.533
It's an electrode
from an electroencephalogram array.

06:49.742 --> 06:52.244
- A what?
- An EEG helmet.

06:52.328 --> 06:54.955
It monitors electrical activity in the brain.

06:55.748 --> 06:57.374
So it wasn't a bloody dream then, was it?

06:57.458 --> 06:58.667
I knew it.

06:58.751 --> 07:00.043
How long have I been saying this?

07:00.128 --> 07:02.462
We're like lab rats in an illegal experiment.

07:02.672 --> 07:04.840
Sarah, where was Paul during all this?

07:05.091 --> 07:09.344
Uh, there were doctors, um...
Two or three of them.

07:09.387 --> 07:12.347
He could be in on it though.
Maybe he set it up.

07:12.432 --> 07:15.183
Well, somebody must be
watching the lab rats. Someone we know.

07:15.393 --> 07:17.978
Well, I mean,
if it were my experiment...

07:18.020 --> 07:20.856
Yeah, I would put an observer close to the
subject, you know, somebody to...

07:21.649 --> 07:24.359
Keep tabs and accumulate data.

07:24.569 --> 07:27.279
Cosima, what'd they do to me?

07:28.281 --> 07:32.367
I think you'd know if they'd
done anything really, um, invasive.

07:32.410 --> 07:34.536
- Oh, my God!
- I'm just saying...

07:34.579 --> 07:38.540
An EEG is like a neurological
test and that mark on your arm looks like...

07:39.292 --> 07:42.002
A blood sample. it sounds diagnostic.

07:42.086 --> 07:44.880
With Paul in on it... I don't know.

07:45.006 --> 07:47.132
Why? Just because he slept with you?

07:47.758 --> 07:48.884
Fe.

07:53.306 --> 07:55.307
Yeah, we sort of ended up shagging.

07:55.683 --> 07:58.518
Dude, that's complex.

07:58.769 --> 08:00.729
You slept with Beth's boyfriend?

08:02.565 --> 08:03.607
Oh!

08:04.358 --> 08:06.026
Far be it for me.

08:08.362 --> 08:10.238
I may be sleeping with my spy as well.

08:11.657 --> 08:13.909
There's the gun you wanted. I've got to go.

08:14.202 --> 08:15.494
Aye, aye, where's the money?

08:16.037 --> 08:18.497
What's it for?

08:19.332 --> 08:21.625
It's a self-defence fund, yeah?

08:21.959 --> 08:24.127
Last time I checked,
I'm the only one defending us.

08:30.510 --> 08:32.427
Here's 20,000.

08:34.514 --> 08:35.931
Please use it wisely.

08:36.015 --> 08:37.474
Yeah, I'll bring you the receipts.

08:39.101 --> 08:41.895
I'm gonna shoot Paul's balls off.

08:41.938 --> 08:44.188
Wait, just squeeze them, okay.

08:44.273 --> 08:45.690
He's our way into this whole thing.

08:46.067 --> 08:48.944
But if my blind subject
were suddenly to become...

08:49.946 --> 08:54.115
Self aware.
It'd either be a eureka moment or...

08:55.409 --> 08:56.618
Yeah?

08:56.786 --> 09:01.289
I would terminate. So, be careful, okay?

09:01.457 --> 09:02.749
On that note...

09:03.876 --> 09:06.294
--Shit!

09:07.838 --> 09:10.549
- Cop station, third time today.
- No, don't answer that.

09:10.633 --> 09:12.384
Uh, Art, what do you want?

09:12.802 --> 09:13.927
It's Raj.

09:15.054 --> 09:16.137
Um...

09:16.973 --> 09:18.473
I'm off the force, Raj.

09:18.683 --> 09:20.642
I know. You okay?

09:21.310 --> 09:22.811
- Yeah.
- Okay, well,

09:22.853 --> 09:24.563
you know that surveillance shit I lent you?

09:25.189 --> 09:26.856
I'm gonna need that back
before they inventory.

09:27.149 --> 09:28.316
Surveillance shit?

09:28.484 --> 09:29.651
Right. Right!

09:30.152 --> 09:31.486
And Beth, level with me.

09:31.571 --> 09:33.405
This is just about Paul, right?

09:33.489 --> 09:36.157
Look, I'll get it back to you
in a couple of days. Okay?

09:39.495 --> 09:41.329
So Beth had surveillance equipment.

09:42.081 --> 09:43.957
So then she was on to Paul too.

09:44.250 --> 09:45.875
Question is, did she find anything?

09:46.836 --> 09:50.547
It's critical. One week
she's fine, the next it's Armageddon.

09:51.299 --> 09:54.759
No, I understand that. But I don't
want to give her any reason to react.

09:56.637 --> 09:59.889
You tell me.
If it gets any worse, what are our options?

10:00.933 --> 10:02.684
What are you doing?

10:03.019 --> 10:04.686
- I have to call you back.
- Why...

10:05.021 --> 10:06.229
Why were you in my vanity?

10:06.355 --> 10:08.023
