10:21.037 --> 10:23.121
- About me?
- About Susan Teller.

10:23.372 --> 10:25.332
She's all over us this quarter. You know that.

10:26.834 --> 10:29.919
Oh, good. Um, can you cut this tag off?
It's driving me crazy.

10:35.217 --> 10:36.551
That's better.

10:43.768 --> 10:45.769
All right.
What do we do if he walks in?

10:45.895 --> 10:47.228
Shoot him.

10:48.064 --> 10:49.856
I'm kidding. Just...

10:50.358 --> 10:52.734
Find the surveillance stuff, yeah?

10:53.027 --> 10:55.236
And put everything back where you found it.

10:55.905 --> 10:57.864
This place is antiseptic.

10:58.449 --> 11:00.909
Paul's whole world feels fake now?

11:02.578 --> 11:03.703
What?

11:04.080 --> 11:05.622
I don't leave prints when I burgle.

11:17.009 --> 11:18.760
"Trexcom Consulting."

11:23.683 --> 11:26.601
if fake Paul is observing Beth,

11:26.686 --> 11:29.354
what makes you so certain
no one's observing Sarah Manning?

11:29.689 --> 11:33.608
Who? Mrs. S hates me,
I haven't seen her in a year

11:34.276 --> 11:36.277
and I'm giving you the benefit of the doubt.

11:36.612 --> 11:38.405
A ringing vote of confidence.

11:41.867 --> 11:44.077
Nothing. On Beth's computer, nothing.

11:44.120 --> 11:47.706
No audio files, no video, no transcripts.

11:52.128 --> 11:53.795
Holy shit!

11:54.130 --> 11:55.797
Hey, hey. Hey.

12:06.058 --> 12:07.267
He's military.

12:12.481 --> 12:14.399
Looks like you're not
the only one keeping secrets.

12:15.401 --> 12:16.943
What are those?

12:17.486 --> 12:18.653
Letters from Beth.

12:18.779 --> 12:21.990
- To Paul? I wanna read them.
- Ah, ah, ah. No, they're private.

12:24.326 --> 12:26.661
Where the hell is his surveillance stuff?

12:26.996 --> 12:29.122
I don't know. We searched everywhere.

12:37.506 --> 12:38.923
There we go.

12:43.721 --> 12:45.680
She wasn't messing around, was she?

12:47.516 --> 12:49.684
Maybe it's time to check out
where Paul works.

12:50.186 --> 12:52.103
Oh, yeah. Trexcom Consulting.

12:52.521 --> 12:54.022
Fake Paul, fake company.

12:54.106 --> 12:56.691
I bet you money there's nothing there.

13:19.799 --> 13:21.549
No way.

13:29.391 --> 13:30.475
Beth?

13:32.353 --> 13:33.603
