13:48.244 --> 13:50.286
I brought him some lunch as a peace offering.

13:51.330 --> 13:52.580
Come on.

14:11.642 --> 14:12.851
I'll just...

14:13.352 --> 14:14.602
Sure.

14:43.841 --> 14:45.592
Big Boob Blowies?

15:03.652 --> 15:05.320
Felix, I hope you can hear this.

15:05.404 --> 15:06.863
Yes. Yeah, well, I can now.

15:06.947 --> 15:09.657
You silly bitch,
would you get your fanny out of there.

15:47.655 --> 15:49.530
- You brought me lunch?
- Yeah.

15:49.865 --> 15:51.115
Olive branch.

15:51.825 --> 15:53.159
About this morning.

15:53.661 --> 15:55.286
You wanna talk about it?

15:59.833 --> 16:01.793
I'd rather talk about last night.

16:01.877 --> 16:04.045
- In the shower.
- Paul...

16:04.964 --> 16:06.839
I came to bring you lunch, that's all.

16:10.886 --> 16:12.762
Something's changed both of us.

16:12.930 --> 16:14.889
Hmm...

16:15.349 --> 16:16.724
I know you can feel it.

16:19.228 --> 16:20.645
What happened to your scar?

16:21.981 --> 16:22.981
What?

16:23.065 --> 16:25.191
The scar on your neck
from the mountain bike crash.

16:25.317 --> 16:26.317
It's gone.

16:27.569 --> 16:29.237
Oh. Really?

16:31.490 --> 16:33.408
I'm using a new lotion.

16:35.911 --> 16:36.995
Let me see.

16:38.664 --> 16:40.581
You'll try anything, won't you?

16:40.791 --> 16:42.000
I will.

16:44.253 --> 16:46.671
But I gotta get back to work.

16:48.549 --> 16:49.799
Thanks for lunch.

16:51.468 --> 16:53.261
- See you tonight.
- Okay.

17:29.506 --> 17:30.923
Madison?

17:33.260 --> 17:34.802
Clear my afternoon. Okay?

17:34.970 --> 17:37.221
- Something came up.
- Shit.

17:48.358 --> 17:50.026
Alison? What are you doing?

17:55.157 --> 17:56.157
Ah...

17:57.826 --> 17:59.702
What's in the box, Donnie?

18:00.287 --> 18:01.454
It's private.

18:01.997 --> 18:04.332
No, it isn't. What is it? What is in it?

18:04.666 --> 18:07.668
- Tell me what's in the box.
- I'm entitled to a little privacy.

18:07.753 --> 18:10.505
- Even in this house.
- Oh! That's rich coming from you.

18:10.964 --> 18:13.257
- What the hell's that supposed to mean?
- Open the box, Donnie.

18:14.051 --> 18:16.177
- Give it to me!
- Open it!

18:16.762 --> 18:17.970
Alison.

18:18.138 --> 18:19.722
Alison, stop it!

18:41.078 --> 18:43.663
Yeah, blood looks fine. No infection.

18:43.997 --> 18:45.706
What kind of symptoms are we talking about?

18:45.874 --> 18:49.877
Um... Shortness of breath,
coughing up blood...

18:50.462 --> 18:52.880
- That sort of thing.
- Who's the subject?

18:53.215 --> 18:54.757
Uh, subject...

18:55.300 --> 18:58.219
