19:01.056 --> 19:05.226
And can you run a PCR on these samples.
See if there are any genetic markers?

19:05.894 --> 19:09.105
You're thinking antitrypsin deficiency,
cystic fibrosis.

19:09.189 --> 19:10.481
Yeah, that kind of thing.

19:10.774 --> 19:11.899
And, um...

19:12.192 --> 19:14.652
- Can you sequence for Cytochrome C?
- The barcode gene?

19:14.736 --> 19:15.736
Mmm-hmm.

19:15.779 --> 19:18.072
That's the one we use
for species differentiation.

19:19.116 --> 19:20.241
Is it?

19:20.742 --> 19:23.411
What's in it for me?

19:24.538 --> 19:27.081
Um, how about you get to have sex...

19:27.583 --> 19:28.749
With yourself?

19:30.752 --> 19:32.628
