20:36.944 --> 20:39.904
Beth loved him but he wouldn't love her back,
and he wouldn't leave her.

20:40.489 --> 20:44.116
Hmm, but he's certainly
changed his tune now, hasn't he?

20:44.868 --> 20:46.661
Sarah, he's falling for you.

20:46.828 --> 20:48.496
- God, what a mess!

20:51.458 --> 20:53.417
I'm outside Kira's school.

20:55.170 --> 20:58.297
Of all the things that scare me right now, Fe,
this one's the heaviest.

20:58.340 --> 21:00.258
You know she can't wait to see you, right?

21:00.342 --> 21:01.342
Yeah, thanks.

21:02.261 --> 21:04.345
She's the only thing
that really matters, you know.

21:06.014 --> 21:07.598
I know, um...

21:07.975 --> 21:09.433
Give her my love, okay.

21:14.606 --> 21:15.940
- Colin.
- Hi.

21:16.024 --> 21:17.692
So glad you could step away.

21:17.818 --> 21:21.028
From the morgue, uh, trust me,
scheduling isn't really an issue.

21:37.713 --> 21:38.921
