22:04.031 --> 22:06.032
You don't miss a thing, do you?

22:10.912 --> 22:12.288
Are you okay, Mommy?

22:13.707 --> 22:15.916
Yeah, I am now.

22:16.251 --> 22:17.835
God, you're so big!

22:17.919 --> 22:20.338
- I'm the smallest kid in my class.

22:22.132 --> 22:23.591
Well, you're big to me.

22:24.760 --> 22:27.762
