22:29.848 --> 22:31.390
She looks just like you.

22:31.767 --> 22:32.975
Yeah.

22:34.102 --> 22:36.812
One day I'll explain it all to you.
Yeah, monkey?

22:37.773 --> 22:39.774
Is someone trying to hurt us?

22:41.276 --> 22:42.568
