22:46.740 --> 22:48.574
- Hey, hey.

22:49.785 --> 22:50.951
No.

22:51.828 --> 22:53.079
We're safe, Kira.

22:54.206 --> 22:56.540
I promise. Okay?

22:56.625 --> 22:58.125
You coming in?

23:22.401 --> 23:25.569
Hey. Sorry. You just forgot
this in the lab. Sorry.

23:25.695 --> 23:27.363
Thank you.

23:27.531 --> 23:30.991
