23:36.123 --> 23:38.290
Thank you. Um, oh, God!

23:38.750 --> 23:41.210
I'm so sorry, I'm not usually like this.

23:41.545 --> 23:43.462
Oh. Bad breakup?

23:44.005 --> 23:47.675
