23:51.930 --> 23:54.598
Um, you're in microbiology too, right?

23:54.724 --> 23:58.561
Yes. Um, immunology.
I study host-parasite relationships.

23:58.645 --> 24:01.355
Oh, cool. Cool, yeah, I'm Evo Devo.

24:03.525 --> 24:07.236
- Evolutionary development.
- Yeah, yeah. That's what we call it here.

24:09.698 --> 24:10.865
Delphine.

24:11.032 --> 24:12.032
Cosima.

24:12.325 --> 24:15.578
EnchantÃ©e.

24:18.874 --> 24:20.374
