24:21.376 --> 24:22.376
Hmm, monkey?

24:22.878 --> 24:24.587
- Little monkey.
- Remind you of anyone?

24:24.713 --> 24:27.214
Yeah, but I was much angrier, wasn't I?

24:28.341 --> 24:29.675
Even small.

24:31.678 --> 24:33.888
You were the one
who introduced me to punk rock, though.

24:35.390 --> 24:39.935
