have to bounce around like I did.

24:47.611 --> 24:49.904
I was her age when
I came to live with you in London, yeah?

24:50.197 --> 24:52.198
- Little bit older.
- Well.

24:53.575 --> 24:55.493
You got me this far.

24:57.245 --> 24:58.496
I know that.

25:01.291 --> 25:03.959
- I still need your help though.
- Ah.

25:05.086 --> 25:06.962
I need you to tell me

25:07.714 --> 25:09.840
what you really know about me.

25:10.592 --> 25:11.759
Where I came from?

25:12.010 --> 25:13.177
Why now?

25:13.261 --> 25:14.803
Trying to square things away.

25:15.430 --> 25:16.680
For Kira, you know.

25:17.682 --> 25:19.767
You're part of the foster system. I took in kids.

25:19.851 --> 25:22.102
You know, I don't know who
your parents were.

25:22.270 --> 25:23.896
Yeah, I talked to

25:24.648 --> 25:28.734
