25:36.576 --> 25:37.910
What about Vic?

25:38.620 --> 25:40.663
- Vic still in the picture?
- God, no.

25:42.415 --> 25:45.084
That much I can promise. Vic is done.

25:54.511 --> 25:55.970
How you doing, boss?

25:56.179 --> 25:57.846
